Name: Decabristov Street
About the game: Take a walk through one of the courtyards of the city of Moscow on Dekabristov Street. Four houses surrounding the yard, a skating rink in the middle, a few garages and solitude... There are no goals or objectives in the game. Control: WASD-walking Space - jump Ctrl - croach F-Drag and drop items E - Opening doors
